 Innes|Innes]] 53' \n|-style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|33||1 May 1999||[[Motherwell F.C.|Motherwell]]||H||0\u20131||8,867||\n|-style=\"background: #FFFFCC;\"\n|34||8 May 1999||[[Dundee United F.C.|Dundee United]]||A||0\u20130||7,190||\n|-style=\"background: #FFFFCC;\"\n|35||15 May 1999||[[St Johnstone F.C.|St Johnstone]]||H||1\u20131||15,086||[[Mark Roberts (footballer, born 1975)|Roberts]] 8'\n|-style=\"background: #FFFFCC;\"\n|36||23 May 1999||[[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]]||A||1\u20131||48,886||[[Kevin McGowne|McGowne]] 41'\n|}\n\n===Scottish Cup===\n{{Main article|1998\u201399 Scottish Cup}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align:center\"\n!Match!!Date!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers\n|-style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|R3||23 January 1999||[[Ayr United F.C.|Ayr United]]||A||0\u20133||10,153||\n|}\n\n===Scottish League Cup===\n{{Main article|1998\u201399 Scottish League Cup}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align:center\"\n!Match!!Date!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|R3||18 August 1998||[[Livingston F.C.|Livingston]]||H||3\u20131||6,565||[[Paul Wright (footballer)|Wright]] 25, 116', [[Ally McCoist|McCoist]] 92'\n|-style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|R4||8 September 1998||[[Airdrieonians F.C. (1878)|Airdrieonians]]||H||0\u20131||7,900||\n|}\n\n===UEFA Cup===\n{{Main article|1998\u201399 UEFA Cup}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%; text-align:center\"\n!Match!!Date!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers\n|-style=\"background: #FFFFCC;\"\n|QR1 1st leg||22 July 1998||[[FK \u017deljezni\u010dar Sarajevo|\u017deljezni\u010dar]]||A||1\u20131||15,000||[[Kevin McGowne|McGowne]] 55'\n|-style=\"background: #CCFFCC;\"\n|QR1 2nd leg||29 July 1998||[[FK \u017deljezni\u010dar Sarajevo|\u017deljezni\u010dar]]||H||1\u20130||14,512||[[Alan Mahood|Mahood]] 31'\n|-style=\"background: #FFCCCC;\"\n|QR2 1st leg||11 August 1998||[[SK Sigma Olomouc|Sigma Olomouc]]||